<plot>An entry in Vitaphone's "Melody Master Bands" series, featuring Harry Owens and His Royal Hawaiians Orchestra, the house band at The Royal Hawaiian Hotel. In addition to some hula dancing and shots of various location in the islands, the music was all-Hawaiian themed and included: "Happy Hawaiian Holiday," "Hula Rhumba," "Aloha'" "Song of the Sea," and "The Laughing Song."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?230881</url></doc>
